  <summary>Sets the <property tag="lockCursor">lockCursor</property> <glossary tag="property">property</glossary> to false, allowing the <property tag="cursor">cursor</property> shape to change normally depending on what the <glossary tag="mouse pointer">mouse pointer</glossary> is over.</summary>
